<p>It is possible that your Wi-Fi adapter will not be working. Or, it might
not be working properly.</p>

<p>For example, you might not be able to authenticate to Wi-Fi networks. Or,
your connection might sometimes disconnect.</p>

<p>If you experience problems with your Wi-Fi adapter, you might be able to
fix them by using an external Wi-Fi adapter or by using a
<a href="http://us.dlink.com/resource-centre/how-to-guides/how-to-extend-your-network-with-a-wireless-bridge/">wireless
bridge</a>.</p>

